{"tid":1956010,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紐約市長呼籲民眾外出時應戴口罩","createTime":"2020-04-03T01:29:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T01:34:49.000Z","uid":194621,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"df6e14da6e8326e05a00d257917d30f84ce2d222","tid":1956010,"uid":194621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T01:29:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國紐約市長白思豪呼籲，所有民眾在外出時應戴上口罩，但不鼓勵購買外科手術口罩或專業口罩，而是鼓勵使用已有的物資或利用不同的材料在家製作，相信使用圍巾或手帕之類的任何東西都行得通，<br />\n<br />\n白思豪表示，研究表明無症狀的人士正在傳播病毒，又承認新的預防措施不符合當初的衛生指示。當被問到為甚麼不提早提出配戴口罩的建議時，白思豪稱沒有證據口罩能預防病毒，並且不希望當地搶購口罩。<br />\n<br />\n另外，美國白宮表示，總統特朗普第二次對新型冠狀病毒檢測呈陰性。特朗普稱，今次是使用新快篩試劑，15分鐘就可以有結果。<br />\n<br />\n紐約市目前確診數目增至5.18萬宗，死亡人數逾1,500人。(mn/t)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.1006493/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.1006493%2F2&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BnpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=89dea712\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.1006493/2</a>"},{"pid":"a54ca2ec80652bb97ca1c950784fcb7e15cf819c","tid":1956010,"uid":194621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T01:34:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}